Dump absolute mean curvature (AMC) around a distance of 3mm and apply heat kernel
diffusion filter with FWHM of 20mm
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAT_DumpAbsMeanCurv name.obj 20mm_curv_name.txt 20 3

Compare AMC values between two samples which are saved in sep. folders sample1
and sample2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAT_GLM_Estimate sample1/20mm_curv*.txt + sample2/20mm_curv*.txt

Calculate means and difference sample1-sample2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAT_GLM_MATH diff_1_vs_2.txt beta_0001.txt - beta_0002.txt
mv beta_0001.txt avg1.txt
mv beta_0002.txt avg2.txt 

Calculate T-test sample1-sample2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAT_GLM_MATH T_1_vs_2.txt T_0001.txt - T_0002.txt

Colourcode results with opacity of 0.8 to visualize with MNI-tools "Display"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAT_Color2Surf avg_12.obj T_1_vs_2.txt T_1_vs_2.obj spectral -5 5 BLACK WHITE 0.8